<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Sri Sai Venkateswara Engineering - Mydukur</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tiro+Telugu&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Noto+Sans+Telugu:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --blue: #1a4fa0;
    --blue-dark: #0d2f6e;
    --blue-light: #2e6fd4;
    --gold: #e8a020;
    --gold-light: #f5c04a;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --off-white: #f4f7ff;
    --text: #1a1a2e;
    --text-muted: #5a6a8a;
    --shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,79,160,0.15);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    color: var(--text);
    background: var(--white);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ---- NAV ---- */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(10,30,80,0.97);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 5%;
    height: 64px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .nav-brand {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  }
  .nav-brand .logo-circle {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue-dark); font-size: 18px;
  }
  .nav-brand span {
    color: var(--white); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }

  /* ---- HERO ---- */
  #hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-dark) 0%, var(--blue) 55%, #2563b0 100%);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 100px 5% 60px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg-pattern {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(232,160,32,0.12) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-grid-lines {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }
  .hero-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease both;
  }
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(36px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(232,160,32,0.18);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .hero-title .gold { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .hero-telugu {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans Telugu', 'Tiro Telugu', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.7rem);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .hero-sub .te {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans Telugu', serif;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 40px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }
  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    margin-top: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 14px 34px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-top: 10px;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(232,160,32,0.35);
  }
  .hero-cta:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  /* ---- SECTION BASE ---- */
  section { padding: 80px 5%; }
  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(26,79,160,0.08);
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .section-title-te {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans Telugu', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .section-divider {
    width: 56px; height: 4px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  /* ---- ABOUT ---- */
  #about { background: var(--off-white); }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-size: 0.97rem;
  }
  .about-text .telugu-p {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans Telugu', serif;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: #7a8aaa;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding-left: 14px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .about-cards {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px;
  }
  .about-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px 18px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--blue);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .about-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .about-card .icon { font-size: 1.9rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .about-card h4 { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue-dark); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .about-card p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ---- SERVICES ---- */
  #services { background: var(--white); }
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 22px;
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .service-card {
    background: var(--off-white);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 30px 22px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1.5px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--blue-light);
    background: var(--white);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }
  .service-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .service-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue-dark); margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .service-card .te { font-family: 'Noto Sans Telugu', serif; font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .service-card p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ---- PARTNERS ---- */
  #partners {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-dark) 0%, var(--blue) 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  #partners .section-tag { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--gold-light); }
  #partners .section-title { color: var(--white); }
  #partners .section-title-te { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  #partners .section-divider { margin: 0 auto 32px; }
  .partners-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 30px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .partner-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 30px 40px;
    min-width: 220px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .partner-card:hover { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .partner-logo {
    width: 80px; height: 80px;
    background: var(--blue);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: white;
  }
  .partner-logo.astral {
    background: #1a4fa0;
  }
  .partner-logo.gajraj {
    background: #c0392b;
  }
  .partner-card h3 { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--blue-dark); }
  .partner-card p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-align: center; }
  .certified-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(232,160,32,0.15);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 3px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ---- CONTACT ---- */
  #contact { background: var(--off-white); }
  .contact-wrapper {
    max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .contact-info { }
  .contact-item {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(26,79,160,0.08);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
  }
  .contact-item .ci-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .contact-item h4 { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue-dark); margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .contact-item p, .contact-item a {
    font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .contact-item a:hover { color: var(--blue); }
  .contact-item .te { font-family: 'Noto Sans Telugu', serif; font-size: 0.82rem; color: #a0aec0; }
  .map-container {
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    height: 340px;
  }
  .map-container iframe {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none;
  }
  .map-placeholder {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8eef8, #c8d8f0);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .map-placeholder .map-pin { font-size: 3rem; }
  .map-placeholder p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--blue); font-weight: 600; text-align: center; padding: 0 20px; }
  .map-placeholder a {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--blue);
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 22px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .map-placeholder a:hover { background: var(--blue-dark); }

  /* ---- FOOTER ---- */
  footer {
    background: var(--blue-dark);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 28px 5%;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  footer .footer-brand { font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold-light); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  footer .footer-te { font-family: 'Noto Sans Telugu', serif; font-size: 0.82rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }

  /* ---- RESPONSIVE ---- */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .about-grid, .contact-wrapper { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; }
    .hero-stats { gap: 24px; }
    .about-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .map-container { height: 280px; }
  }

  /* scroll reveal */
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-brand">
    <div class="logo-circle">🔩</div>
    <span>Sri Sai Venkateswara<br>Engineering</span>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#hero">Home</a>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#partners">Partners</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg-pattern"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid-lines"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">✅ Certified Borewell & Engineering Shop · Mydukur</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Sri Sai <span class="gold">Venkateswara</span><br>Engineering</h1>
    <p class="hero-telugu">శ్రీ సాయి వెంకటేశ్వర ఇంజినీరింగ్</p>
    <p class="hero-sub">Your trusted borewell & motor pump experts in Mydukur with over 15 years of experience.</p>
    <p class="hero-sub te">మైడుకూర్‌లో 15+ సంవత్సరాల విశ్వసనీయ బోర్‌వెల్ & మోటార్ పంప్ నిపుణులు.</p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">15+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Years Experience<br>సంవత్సరాల అనుభవం</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">2</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Certified Brands<br>సర్టిఫైడ్ బ్రాండ్లు</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">7</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Days Open<br>రోజులు తెరిచి ఉంటాం</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="tel:9949801904" class="hero-cta">📞 Call Now: 9949801904</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <span class="section-tag">About Us · మా గురించి</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">15+ Years of Trusted<br>Borewell Expertise</h2>
      <p class="section-title-te">15+ సంవత్సరాల విశ్వసనీయమైన బోర్‌వెల్ అనుభవం</p>
      <div class="section-divider"></div>
      <p>Sri Sai Venkateswara Engineering has been serving the Mydukur community for over 15 years. We specialize in borewell drilling, motor pump installation, repair, and maintenance — offering honest, reliable service every single day.</p>
      <p>We are an authorized dealer and certified service center for Astral Pipes and Gajraj Motor Pumps, ensuring you receive only genuine parts and professional expertise.</p>
      <p class="telugu-p">మేము మైడుకూర్ సమాజానికి 15 సంవత్సరాలకు పైగా సేవలందిస్తున్నాము. బోర్‌వెల్ డ్రిల్లింగ్, మోటార్ పంప్ ఇన్‌స్టాలేషన్, మరమ్మత్తు మరియు నిర్వహణలో మేము నిపుణులం.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-cards reveal">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="icon">🏅</div>
        <h4>Certified Shop</h4>
        <p>Authorized dealer for top brands in the region.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="icon">🕘</div>
        <h4>Open Every Day</h4>
        <p>Mon–Sun, 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM.<br>ప్రతి రోజూ తెరిచి ఉంటాం.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="icon">⚙️</div>
        <h4>All Borewell Work</h4>
        <p>New drilling, casing, repairs — all under one roof.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="icon">🤝</div>
        <h4>Honest Service</h4>
        <p>Fair pricing, quality parts, trusted by hundreds.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section id="services">
  <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom: 40px;" class="reveal">
    <span class="section-tag">Our Services · మా సేవలు</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">What We Do</h2>
    <p class="section-title-te">మేము అందించే సేవలు</p>
    <div class="section-divider" style="margin: 0 auto;"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-card reveal">
      <div class="service-icon">🌀</div>
      <h3>Borewell Drilling</h3>
      <p class="te">బోర్‌వెల్ డ్రిల్లింగ్</p>
      <p>New borewell drilling with modern equipment for homes, farms & commercial use.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card reveal">
      <div class="service-icon">🔧</div>
      <h3>Borewell Repairs</h3>
      <p class="te">బోర్‌వెల్ మరమ్మత్తు</p>
      <p>Quick, reliable repair services for existing borewells. All depths covered.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card reveal">
      <div class="service-icon">💧</div>
      <h3>Motor Pump Installation</h3>
      <p class="te">మోటార్ పంప్ ఇన్‌స్టాలేషన్</p>
      <p>Expert installation of submersible and surface motor pumps for all needs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card reveal">
      <div class="service-icon">🛠️</div>
      <h3>Pump Repairs & Service</h3>
      <p class="te">పంప్ మరమ్మత్తు</p>
      <p>Servicing and repairs for all types of motor pumps. Fast turnaround guaranteed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card reveal">
      <div class="service-icon">🔩</div>
      <h3>Astral Pipes Supply</h3>
      <p class="te">ఆస్ట్రల్ పైప్స్ సరఫరా</p>
      <p>Genuine Astral pipes for borewell casing, plumbing, and water supply.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card reveal">
      <div class="service-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Electrical Motor Work</h3>
      <p class="te">విద్యుత్ మోటార్ పని</p>
      <p>Winding, rewinding, and electrical maintenance for all motors.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PARTNERS -->
<section id="partners">
  <div class="reveal">
    <span class="section-tag">Our Partners · మా భాగస్వాములు</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Collaborating with Trusted Brands</h2>
    <p class="section-title-te">విశ్వసనీయమైన బ్రాండ్లతో సహకారం</p>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width:560px; margin: 0 auto 36px; font-size:0.95rem;">
      We are proud to be an authorized, certified shop for these industry-leading brands — ensuring quality you can trust.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="partners-row reveal">
    <div class="partner-card">
      <div class="partner-logo astral">🔺</div>
      <h3>Astral Pipes</h3>
      <p>India's leading pipe manufacturer. Genuine Astral pipes for borewells & plumbing.</p>
      <span class="certified-badge">✅ Certified Dealer</span>
    </div>
    <div class="partner-card">
      <div class="partner-logo gajraj">🐘</div>
      <h3>Gajraj Motor Pumps</h3>
      <p>Trusted motor pump brand for agriculture, domestic & industrial applications.</p>
      <span class="certified-badge">✅ Certified Dealer</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTACT -->
<section id="contact">
  <div style="margin-bottom: 40px;" class="reveal">
    <span class="section-tag">Contact Us · సంప్రదించండి</span>
